Package: arandr
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python-setuptools, x11-xserver-utils
Description: Simple visual front end for XRandR 1.2
 ARandR is a visual front end for XRandR 1.2 (per display options), which provides full controll over positioning, saving and loading to/from shell scripts and easy integration with other applications.
